        <h2 id="section-5">Open Questions</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>How does the dust destruction rate depend on outflow velocity and composition?</li>
            <li>What is the total dust mass in AGN outflows, and does it significantly affect metallicity and dust depletion?</li>
            <li>How do outflow PAH properties evolve with AGN luminosity and host galaxy mass?</li>
            <li>Can the same kinematic techniques be applied to other dust features to study grain size distributions in outflows?</li>
            <li>What fraction of AGN-driven mass outflows includes dust, and how does this vary across AGN types?</li>
        </ul>

